---
By: Sogyal Rinpoche
Locus:
  Page: 114
  Verse: 1
Tags:
  - Duality
---
ispr - Two people have been living in you all of your life. One is the ego,
garrulous, demanding, hysterical, calculating; the other is the hidden
spiritual being, whose still voice of wisdom you have only rarely heard or
attended to.
